author: brane
msg: Update the vcproj generator to get it working and refactor a bit of code
into the Windows generator base class.
Patch by: D.J. Heap <dj@shadyvale.net>
* build/generator/msvc_dsp.ezt:
Changed dsp_name to proj_name as part of refactoring.
* build/generator/gen_vcnet_vcproj.py:
Mostly rewritten, using gen_msvc_dsp.py as a basis.
* build/generator/vcnet_vcproj.ezt:
Updated template with new generator parameters.
* build/generator/gen_win.py
(adjust_win_depends): added this new method to base generator
to refactor code from vcproj and dsp generators -- it handles
some special dependency cases.
(gen_proj_names): added this as part of refactoring also -- it
handles generator project names.
* build/generator/gen_msvc_dsp.py:
Renamed dsp_name to proj_name as part of code refactoring throughout
the file.
(write): Removed code that was refactored into the
adjust_win_depends method of the base class.

author: cmpilato
msg: For days he makes his way, to and fro across the wilderness.  He moves
with power, with grace, and with purpose -- hungry, wanting, yet ever
patient.  Entire species banished to a terrestrial existance evade --
fear -- the sweeping shadow that blots, if only for an eternal moment,
the joyous warmth of a benevolent sun.
But there!  A shudder in brush, a tremble in a shaft of weed.  The
very silence of the dusty dawn calls out, "Take heed, little one, for
the eagle Stein is about!"
Dinner, it would seem, is served.
A followup to revision 6302.
* subversion/libsvn_delta/path_driver.c
(svn_delta_path_driver): Treat constified strings with proper respect.
* subversion/libsvn_repos/commit.c
(struct file_baton): Remove 'pool'.
(add_file, open_file): No longer populate the file_baton's pool
member (it ain't thay no mo').

author: jerenkrantz
msg: Fix mod_dav_svn's autoversioning where a PUT would fail because activities
could only be in !svn, and autoversioning attempts to create activities in
the current location.
* subversion/mod_dav_svn/version.c
(dav_svn_checkout): Move the setting of resource->info->auto_checked_out to
before dav_svn_make_activity.
(dav_svn_can_be_activity): If a resource is auto_checked_out, then it can
be an activity.  As only dav_svn_checkout will set this to true, we know
that the only path where it is true is from autoversioning.
Review by: Ben Collins-Sussman <sussman@collab.net>
Sander Striker <striker@apache.org>
